badsmtp (0.1.2-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * SMTP test server for development and CI/CD
  * Support for multiple authentication mechanisms
  * Port-based behaviour system for testing
  * Error simulation capabilities
  * Maildir-format message storage
  * TLS/STARTTLS support

